随后引起约20人上街头游行要求日本领事馆交代<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guancha.cn/local/2016_05_31_362319.shtml |title=香港粉丝抗议神奇宝贝改名 上街头游行要求日本领事馆交代 |accessdate=2016-06-02 |archive-date=2016-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603164602/http://www.guancha.cn/local/2016_05_31_362319.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。事件发酵后任天堂表示可能取消首届在香港举办的「2016 Poké-{}-mon Video Game National Championships」的香港区赛事<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamersky.com/news/201605/758913.shtml |title=香港玩家请愿将皮卡丘改回比卡超 任天堂果断否决 |accessdate=2016-06-02 |archive-date=2019-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517085055/https://www.gamersky.com/news/201605/758913.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamersky.com/news/201606/759433.shtml |title=香港玩家要求皮卡丘改回比卡超被拒 或取消国际赛事 |accessdate=2016-06-02 |archive-date=2019-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517085426/https://www.gamersky.com/news/201606/759433.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最终任天堂表态将延期比赛到7月3日举办<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamersky.com/news/201606/760538.shtml |title=《精灵宝可梦》香港国际电玩赛确认延期 |accessdate=2016-06-03 |archive-date=2019-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517085506/https://www.gamersky.com/news/201606/760538.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.com.hk/pressrelease/3ds_20160510_wcs2016.htm |title=2016 Pokémon World Championships Hong Kong Video Game National Championships |accessdate=2016-05-12 |archive-date=2019-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517085600/https://www.nintendo.com.hk/pressrelease/3ds_20160510_wcs2016.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

